---
const reasons = [
	{
		title: 'You get a straight answer early',
		copy:
			'Most clients are trying to figure out whether the matter is worth pursuing, what it may cost, and what should happen next. The goal is to answer that clearly instead of dragging things out.',
	},
	{
		title: 'You are not dropped into a generic intake loop',
		copy:
			'New matters are reviewed with attention to fit, timing, and whether the work actually belongs here. That helps good clients move forward faster and helps the firm say no when the fit is wrong.',
	},
	{
		title: 'You should know the path before you commit',
		copy:
			'Whether the issue involves injury, planning, family, or business documents, clients should understand the likely next step before more time or money is spent.',
	},
];
---

<section class="section-xl">
	<div class="shell">
		<div class="section-head">
			<div>
				<p class="eyebrow">Why Choose</p>
				<h2 class="section-title">Why Choose Cinocca Law?</h2>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="grid-3 why-choose-grid">
			{
				reasons.map((item, index) => (
					<div class="why-card">
						<p class="why-number">{String(index + 1).padStart(2, '0')}</p>
						<h3>{item.title}</h3>
						<p>{item.copy}</p>
					</div>
				))
			}
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
